On a pro forma combined basis, excluding merger and integration expense, intangible amortization expense, the CDO write-down, and non-operating items in the fourth quarter of 2006 and third quarter of 2007 (detailed in the Quarterly Earnings Summary), we generated 1,050 bps of positive operating leverage compared to the prior year and 350 bps sequentially.
 
 
 
 
 
 
