The was a negative 15.5%. The negative tax rate reflects the absolute level of charges associated with the support agreements, securities losses and the final SILO/LILO settlement, as well as the settlement of prior tax audit cycles. Excluding these items, as well as M&I expenses, the effective tax rate was 32.4% in the third quarter of 2008.
