The was 30.6% in the fourth quarter of 2011, compared with 27.3% on a continuing operations basis in the fourth quarter of 2010, and 29.7% in the third quarter of 2011. The effective tax rate in the fourth quarter of 2011 was negatively impacted by non-tax deductible goodwill associated with the disposition of Shareowner Services which was largely offset by a more favorable mix of foreign and domestic income.
